Spec: Bootstrap Metadata Service
Purpose:
  Read front matter values from a local SpecDD bootstrap file.

Structure:
  bootstrap-metadata.ts: Bootstrap metadata service implementation.
  bootstrap-metadata.test.ts: Bootstrap metadata service tests.

Owns:
  bootstrap-metadata.ts
  bootstrap-metadata.test.ts

References:
  ../../constants.sdd
  ../../infrastructure/file-system.sdd

Must:
  Accept FileSystem through the constructor.
  Check whether .specdd/bootstrap.md exists in a target directory.
  Read Version and Changelog front matter values from .specdd/bootstrap.md.
  Strip matching single or double quotes from returned front matter values.

Must not:
  Validate version semantics.
  Modify files.
  Perform network operations.

Depends on:
  FileSystem
  CliError

Exposes:
  BootstrapMetadata
  BootstrapMetadata.hasBootstrap(targetDirectoryPath)
  BootstrapMetadata.readVersion(targetDirectoryPath)
  BootstrapMetadata.readChangelog(targetDirectoryPath)

Raises:
  BootstrapMetadataError
  BootstrapMetadataMissingFieldError
